<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Cheerfully" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Cheerfully,</orth> 1) with good spirits, gladly: <bibl n="shak. shr 4.3.38" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 3, 38</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 4.1.204" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 1, 204</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.1.167" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 1, 167</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.34" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 34</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.4.50" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 50</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 5.3.269" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 269</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.133" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 2, 133</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.5.109" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 5, 109</bibl>.<lb />2) in a comforting and encouraging manner: <cit><quote>thou speakest c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.1.34" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 1, 34</bibl></cit>.
